<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id" data-theme="light">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %> - <%= appName %></title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/app.css">
  <style>
    :root{--d-bg:#eef2f9;--d-card:#fff;--d-border:#e0e7f3;--d-text:#0d1b3e;--d-muted:#6b7fa8;--d-blue1:#1a6ef5;}
    .st-page{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;}
    @keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
    .a1{animation:fadeUp .35s ease both}.a2{animation:fadeUp .35s .07s ease both}.a3{animation:fadeUp .35s .14s ease both}
    .st-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:220px 1fr;gap:20px;align-items:start;}
    @media(max-width:800px){.st-layout{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}
    /* Nav tabs kiri */
    .st-nav{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--d-border);border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;position:sticky;top:78px;}
    .st-nav-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:12px 16px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--d-muted);cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;border-left:3px solid transparent;}
    .st-nav-item:hover{background:#f4f8ff;color:var(--d-blue1);}
    .st-nav-item.active{background:#eff6ff;color:var(--d-blue1);}
    .st-nav-item svg{flex-shrink:0;}
    .st-nav-sep{height:1px;background:var(--d-border);margin:4px 0;}
    /* Content cards */
    .st-section{display:none;} .st-section.show{display:block;}
    .st-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--d-border);border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:14px;}
    .st-card-hdr{padding:16px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--d-border);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8faff,#f0f4ff);}
    .st-card-icon{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:10px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a6ef5,#0047cc);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;}
    .st-card-body{padding:20px;}
    /* Form fields */
    .pf-label{font-size:10.5px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.07em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--d-muted);display:block;margin-bottom:6px;}
    .pf-input,.pf-select{width:100%;padding:10px 12px;border-radius:10px;border:1.5px solid var(--d-border);font-size:13px;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;outline:none;background:#fff;color:var(--d-text);transition:all .15s;}
    .pf-input:focus,.pf-select:focus{border-color:var(--d-blue1);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(26,110,245,.08);}
    .pf-field{margin-bottom:16px;}
    .pf-hint{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--d-muted);margin-top:4px;line-height:1.5;}
    /* Brand mode cards */
    .brand-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:12px;margin-bottom:16px;}
    @media(max-width:600px){.brand-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}
    .brand-option{border:2px solid var(--d-border);border-radius:12px;padding:14px 12px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;text-align:center;background:#fff;position:relative;}
    .brand-option:hover{border-color:#93c5fd;background:#f0f9ff;}
    .brand-option.selected{border-color:var(--d-blue1);background:#eff6ff;}
    .brand-option.selected::after{content:'✓';position:absolute;top:8px;right:10px;font-size:12px;font-weight:800;color:var(--d-blue1);}
    .brand-preview{height:42px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:8px;background:#f8faff;border-radius:8px;padding:0 10px;}
    .brand-preview .mini-icon{width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:6px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a6ef5,#0047cc);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;}
    .brand-option-title{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--d-text);}
    .brand-option-desc{font-size:10.5px;color:var(--d-muted);margin-top:2px;}
    /* Preview box */
    .brand-live-preview{background:#f8faff;border:1.5px solid var(--d-border);border-radius:12px;padding:14px 16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:16px;}
    /* Save button */
    .save-btn{padding:11px 28px;border-radius:11px;font-size:13.5px;font-weight:700;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a6ef5,#0047cc);color:#fff;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;transition:opacity .15s;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;}
    .pf-btn-outline{padding:10px 16px;border-radius:10px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;background:#fff;color:var(--d-text);border:1.5px solid var(--d-border);cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:7px;transition:all .15s;}
    .pf-btn-outline:hover{background:#f8fafc;border-color:#94a3b8;}
    .save-btn:hover{opacity:.9;}
    .divider{height:1px;background:var(--d-border);margin:20px 0;}

    /* ═══ TAX / PPN ═══ */
    .tax-switch{
      width:38px;height:22px;border-radius:20px;background:#cbd5e1;
      position:relative;transition:background .2s;display:inline-block;flex-shrink:0;
    }
    .tax-switch::after{
      content:'';position:absolute;top:2px;left:2px;
      width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;background:#fff;
      box-shadow:0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.15);
      transition:left .2s;
    }
    #taxEnabled:checked + .tax-switch{ background:#0d9488; }
    #taxEnabled:checked + .tax-switch::after{ left:18px; }
    #taxEnabled:focus-visible + .tax-switch{ box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(13,148,136,.25); }

    .tax-preset{
      display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;margin-left:2px;border-radius:6px;
      background:#f1f5f9;color:#475569;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;
      font-size:10.5px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;
      transition:all .15s;
    }
    .tax-preset:hover{ background:#0d9488;color:#fff;border-color:#0d9488; }

    /* Body collapse saat PPN nonaktif */
    #taxCardBody.tax-disabled{ opacity:.55;pointer-events:none; }

    /* Spinner animation untuk tombol recalculate */
    @keyframes spin { from { transform: rotate(0deg); } to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

    /* Auto Generate Invoice toggle (sama pattern dgn tax-switch, warna biru) */
    .autogen-switch{
      width:38px;height:22px;border-radius:20px;background:#cbd5e1;
      position:relative;transition:background .2s;display:inline-block;flex-shrink:0;
    }
    .autogen-switch::after{
      content:'';position:absolute;top:2px;left:2px;
      width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;background:#fff;
      box-shadow:0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.15);
      transition:left .2s;
    }
    #autoGenInvoice:checked + .autogen-switch{ background:#2563eb; }
    #autoGenInvoice:checked + .autogen-switch::after{ left:18px; }
    #autoGenInvoice:focus-visible + .autogen-switch{ box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(37,99,235,.25); }

    /* ═══ PUSH NOTIFICATION STYLES ═══ */
    .push-stat{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8faff,#eff6ff);border:1px solid var(--d-border);border-radius:12px;padding:12px 14px;}
    .push-stat-lbl{font-size:10.5px;color:var(--d-muted);font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;}
    .push-stat-val{font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:var(--d-text);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;margin-top:4px;}

    .push-tab{padding:10px 14px;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;color:var(--d-muted);cursor:pointer;border-bottom:2.5px solid transparent;margin-bottom:-1.5px;transition:all .15s;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;}
    .push-tab svg{width:14px;height:14px;}
    .push-tab:hover{color:var(--d-blue1);}
    .push-tab.active{color:var(--d-blue1);border-bottom-color:var(--d-blue1);}
    .push-tab-content{display:none;}
    .push-tab-content.active{display:block;}

    .push-section-hdr{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--d-text);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;}
    .push-section-hdr svg{width:14px;height:14px;color:var(--d-blue1);}

    @keyframes pushPulse{0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)}50%{opacity:.6;transform:scale(.85)}}

    /* Inline SVG button helpers */
    .push-btn-icon{width:13px;height:13px;vertical-align:-2px;margin-right:4px;}

    .push-chip{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:7px 12px;border:1.5px solid var(--d-border);border-radius:20px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;user-select:none;background:#fff;transition:all .15s;}
    .push-chip:hover{border-color:#93c5fd;background:#f0f9ff;}
    .push-chip input{width:14px;height:14px;cursor:pointer;margin:0;}
    .push-chip:has(input:checked){background:#eff6ff;border-color:var(--d-blue1);color:var(--d-blue1);}

    .push-mini-btn{padding:6px 12px;border-radius:8px;background:#eff6ff;color:var(--d-blue1);border:1px solid #bfdbfe;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;}
    .push-mini-btn:hover{background:#dbeafe;}

    .emoji-chip{width:40px;height:40px;border:1.5px solid var(--d-border);border-radius:10px;background:#fff;font-size:20px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all .15s;}
    .emoji-chip:hover{border-color:var(--d-blue1);background:#eff6ff;transform:scale(1.05);}

    .push-preview{background:#0f172a;color:#fff;border-radius:14px;padding:14px;display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,.25);}
    .push-preview .pp-icon{width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:9px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:20px;flex-shrink:0;}
    .push-preview .pp-body{flex:1;min-width:0;}
    .push-preview .pp-app{font-size:10.5px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);margin-bottom:3px;font-weight:600;}
    .push-preview .pp-title{font-size:13.5px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:3px;word-wrap:break-word;}
    .push-preview .pp-text{font-size:12.5px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);line-height:1.4;word-wrap:break-word;}

    .push-tpl-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--d-border);border-radius:12px;padding:14px;margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;}
    .push-tpl-icon{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:20px;flex-shrink:0;}
    .push-tpl-info{flex:1;min-width:0;}
    .push-tpl-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--d-text);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
    .push-tpl-badge{padding:1.5px 8px;border-radius:20px;font-size:10px;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.4px;}
    .push-tpl-title{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--d-text);margin-top:4px;}
    .push-tpl-body{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--d-muted);margin-top:2px;display:-webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp:2;-webkit-box-orient:vertical;overflow:hidden;}

    .push-hist-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--d-border);border-radius:12px;padding:14px;margin-bottom:10px;}
    .push-hist-head{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;margin-bottom:8px;}
    .push-hist-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--d-text);flex:1;}
    .push-hist-body{font-size:12px;color:var(--d-muted);line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:8px;}
    .push-hist-meta{font-size:11px;color:var(--d-muted);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
    .push-hist-meta b{color:var(--d-text);}
    .push-status-badge{padding:2px 9px;border-radius:20px;font-size:10px;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.4px;}
    .push-status-sent{background:#dcfce7;color:#166534;}
    .push-status-scheduled{background:#dbeafe;color:#1e40af;}
    .push-status-failed{background:#fee2e2;color:#991b1b;}
    .push-status-cancelled{background:#f1f5f9;color:#475569;}
    .push-status-pending{background:#fef3c7;color:#854d0e;}

    .push-cust-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;}
    .push-cust-row:hover{background:#f8faff;}
    .push-cust-row.picked{background:#eff6ff;}
    .push-cust-row input{width:14px;height:14px;cursor:pointer;margin:0;}
    .push-cust-name{flex:1;min-width:0;font-weight:600;color:var(--d-text);}
    .push-cust-meta{font-size:10.5px;color:var(--d-muted);}
    .push-cust-sub{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#10b981;flex-shrink:0;}
    .push-cust-sub.off{background:#cbd5e1;}

    @media(max-width:900px){
      #pushStatsWrap{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)!important;}
      #push-tab-send > div{grid-template-columns:1fr!important;}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="app-layout st-page">
  <%- include('../partials/sidebar') %>
  <div class="main-content">
    <%- include('../partials/topbar') %>
    <main class="page-content">

      <div style="margin-bottom:20px;" class="a1">
        <h1 style="font-size:21px;font-weight:800;color:#0d1b3e;margin:0 0 3px;">Settings</h1>
        <p style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--d-muted);margin:0;">Konfigurasi aplikasi, tampilan, dan preferensi sistem</p>
      </div>

      <div class="st-layout">
        <!-- Nav kiri -->
        <div class="st-nav a2">
          <div class="st-nav-item active" onclick="showSection('brand',this)">
            <svg width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01"/></svg>
            Tampilan & Brand
          </div>
          <div class="st-nav-item" onclick="showSection('general',this)">
            <svg width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 00.33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 010 2.83 2 2 0 01-2.83 0l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 00-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 01-4 0v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 009 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 01-2.83-2.83l.06-.06A1.65 1.65 0 004.68 15a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 010-4h.09A1.65 1.65 0 004.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 00-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 012.83-2.83l.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 009 4.68a1.65 1.65 0 001-1.51V3a2 2 0 014 0v.09a1.65 1.65 0 001 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 001.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 012.83 2.83l-.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0019.4 9a1.65 1.65 0 001.51 1H21a2 2 0 010 4h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.51 1z"/></svg>
            Umum
          </div>
          <div class="st-nav-sep"></div>
          <div class="st-nav-item" onclick="showSection('payment',this)">
            <svg width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="2" y="5" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="2" y1="10" x2="22" y2="10"/></svg>
            Pembayaran
          </div>
          <div class="st-nav-item" onclick="showSection('gateway',this)">
            <svg width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
            Payment Gateway
          </div>
          <div class="st-nav-item" onclick="showSection('push',this)">
            <svg width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18 8A6 6 0 006 8c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9"/><path d="M13.73 21a2 2 0 01-3.46 0"/></svg>
            Push Notification
          </div>
          <div class="st-nav-item" onclick="showSection('announcements',this)">
            <svg width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22 17H2a3 3 0 000 6h20v-6z"/><path d="M6 17V7a2 2 0 012-2h8a2 2 0 012 2v10"/><line x1="12" y1="12" x2="12" y2="17"/></svg>
            Pengumuman Portal
          </div>
          <div class="st-nav-sep"></div>
          <div class="st-nav-item" onclick="window.location='/settings/users'">
            <svg width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H8a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
            Users & Roles
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="a3">

          <!-- BRAND SECTION -->
          <div class="st-section show" id="sec-brand">
            <div class="st-card">
              <div class="st-card-hdr">
                <div class="st-card-icon"><svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01"/></svg></div>
                <div>
                  <div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--d-text);">Tampilan Judul Aplikasi</div>
                  <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--d-muted);">Atur tampilan nama/logo di sidebar</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="st-card-body">

                <!-- Mode selection -->
                <div class="pf-field">
                  <label class="pf-label">Mode Tampilan</label>
                  <%
                    // Preview text — pakai nama/tagline dari setting (fallback ke default)
                    const previewName    = appSettings?.app_name    || 'DIGSnet';
                    const previewTagline = appSettings?.app_tagline || 'ISP Management';
                  %>
                  <div class="brand-grid">
                    <div class="brand-option <%- (appSettings?.brand_mode||'name_tagline')==='name_tagline'?'selected':'' %>" onclick="selectBrand('name_tagline',this)">
                      <div class="brand-preview">
                        <div class="mini-icon"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg></div>
                        <div style="text-align:left;min-width:0;flex:1;overflow:hidden;">
                          <div id="bopt1Name" style="font-size:10px;font-weight:800;color:#0d1b3e;line-height:1.1;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;"><%= previewName %></div>
                          <div id="bopt1Tag"  style="font-size:7.5px;color:#94a3b8;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;"><%= previewTagline %></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="brand-option-title">Nama + Tagline</div>
                      <div class="brand-option-desc">Ikon + nama + tagline kecil</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="brand-option <%- (appSettings?.brand_mode||'')==='name_logo'?'selected':'' %>" onclick="selectBrand('name_logo',this)">
                      <div class="brand-preview">
                        <div style="width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:6px;background:#e2e8f0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:8px;color:#64748b;flex-shrink:0;">IMG</div>
                        <div id="bopt2Name" style="font-size:10px;font-weight:800;color:#0d1b3e;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;min-width:0;flex:1;"><%= previewName %></div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="brand-option-title">Logo + Nama</div>
                      <div class="brand-option-desc">Logo custom + nama teks</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="brand-option <%- (appSettings?.brand_mode||'')==='logo_only'?'selected':'' %>" onclick="selectBrand('logo_only',this)">
                      <div class="brand-preview">
                        <div style="width:80px;height:26px;background:#e2e8f0;border-radius:5px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:8px;color:#64748b;">LOGO</div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="brand-option-title">Logo Only</div>
                      <div class="brand-option-desc">Hanya gambar logo</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <input type="hidden" id="brandMode" value="<%= appSettings?.brand_mode||'name_tagline' %>">
                </div>

                <div class="divider"></div>

                <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;">
                  <div class="pf-field" style="margin-bottom:0;">
                    <label class="pf-label">Nama Aplikasi</label>
                    <input type="text" class="pf-input" id="appName" value="<%= appSettings?.app_name||'DIGSnet' %>" oninput="updatePreview()">
                  </div>
                  <div class="pf-field" style="margin-bottom:0;" id="taglineField">
                    <label class="pf-label">Tagline</label>
                    <input type="text" class="pf-input" id="appTagline" value="<%= appSettings?.app_tagline||'ISP Management' %>" placeholder="ISP Management" oninput="updatePreview()">
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="pf-field" style="margin-top:14px;" id="logoField">
                  <label class="pf-label">Logo Aplikasi <span style="font-weight:400;text-transform:none;color:var(--d-muted);">(PNG/SVG/WebP, maks 2MB)</span></label>

                  <!-- Upload area -->
                  <div id="logoDropArea" onclick="document.getElementById('logoFileInput').click()" ondragover="event.preventDefault();this.style.borderColor='#1a6ef5';" ondragleave="this.style.borderColor='';" ondrop="handleLogoDrop(event)"
                    style="border:2px dashed #e0e7f3;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;margin-bottom:10px;background:#f8faff;">
                    <div id="logoPreviewThumb" style="display:none;margin-bottom:10px;">
                      <img id="logoThumbImg" src="" alt="logo" style="max-height:52px;max-width:160px;object-fit:contain;border-radius:6px;border:1px solid #e0e7f3;padding:4px;background:#fff;">
                    </div>
                    <div id="logoDropText">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5" style="margin-bottom:6px;"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-8l-4-4m0 0L8 8m4-4v12"/></svg>
                      <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#374151;">Klik atau drag & drop logo</div>
                      <div style="font-size:11.5px;color:#94a3b8;margin-top:2px;">PNG, SVG, JPG, WebP — maks 2MB</div>
                    </div>
                    <input type="file" id="logoFileInput" accept=".png,.jpg,.jpeg,.svg,.webp" style="display:none;" onchange="handleLogoFile(this.files[0])">
                  </div>

                  <!-- URL manual -->
                  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;">
                    <div style="flex:1;position:relative;">
                      <input type="text" class="pf-input" id="logoUrl" value="<%= appSettings?.logo_url||'' %>" placeholder="Atau masukkan URL: https://..." oninput="updatePreview()" style="padding-right:80px;">
                      <span style="position:absolute;right:10px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);font-size:10.5px;color:#94a3b8;pointer-events:none;">URL manual</span>
                    </div>
                    <button type="button" onclick="uploadLogo()" id="btnUploadLogo" style="padding:10px 16px;border-radius:9px;border:none;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a6ef5,#0047cc);color:#fff;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;display:none;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;">
                      Upload
                    </button>
                  </div>
                  <div class="pf-hint">Disarankan format PNG/SVG transparan, tinggi 32–40px.</div>
                </div>

                <!-- Favicon Upload -->
                <div class="pf-field" style="margin-top:14px;" id="faviconField">
                  <label class="pf-label">Favicon <span style="font-weight:400;text-transform:none;color:var(--d-muted);">(ICO/PNG/SVG, maks 1MB — tampil di tab browser)</span></label>

                  <div id="faviconDropArea" onclick="document.getElementById('faviconFileInput').click()" ondragover="event.preventDefault();this.style.borderColor='#1a6ef5';" ondragleave="this.style.borderColor='';" ondrop="handleFaviconDrop(event)"
                    style="border:2px dashed #e0e7f3;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;margin-bottom:10px;background:#f8faff;">
                    <div id="faviconPreviewThumb" style="display:<%= appSettings?.favicon_url ? 'block' : 'none' %>;margin-bottom:10px;">
                      <img id="faviconThumbImg" src="<%= appSettings?.favicon_url || '' %>" alt="favicon" style="height:32px;width:32px;object-fit:contain;border-radius:6px;border:1px solid #e0e7f3;padding:3px;background:#fff;">
                      <span style="display:inline-block;margin-left:8px;vertical-align:middle;font-size:12px;color:#374151;font-weight:500;">Favicon aktif</span>
                    </div>
                    <div id="faviconDropText">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5" style="margin-bottom:4px;"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg>
                      <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#374151;">Klik atau drag & drop favicon</div>
                      <div style="font-size:11.5px;color:#94a3b8;margin-top:2px;">ICO, PNG, SVG — ukuran 32×32 atau 64×64 piksel</div>
                    </div>
                    <input type="file" id="faviconFileInput" accept=".ico,.png,.svg,.jpg,.jpeg" style="display:none;" onchange="handleFaviconFile(this.files[0])">
                  </div>

                  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;">
                    <button type="button" onclick="uploadFavicon()" id="btnUploadFavicon" style="padding:9px 16px;border-radius:9px;border:none;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a6ef5,#0047cc);color:#fff;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;display:none;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;">
                      Upload Favicon
                    </button>
                    <button type="button" onclick="resetFavicon()" id="btnResetFavicon" style="padding:9px 16px;border-radius:9px;border:1px solid #e0e7f3;background:#fff;color:#dc2626;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;display:<%= appSettings?.favicon_url ? 'inline-block' : 'none' %>;">
                      Reset ke Default
                    </button>
                  </div>
                  <div class="pf-hint">Setelah upload, refresh halaman (Ctrl+F5) untuk melihat favicon baru di tab browser.</div>
                </div>

                <!-- Live preview -->
                <div class="divider"></div>
                <label class="pf-label">Preview Sidebar</label>
                <div class="brand-live-preview" id="brandPreview">
                  <!-- diisi JS -->
                </div>

                <button class="save-btn" onclick="saveBrandSettings()">
                  <svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                  Simpan Pengaturan
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Portal Customer Hero Image -->
            <div class="st-card" style="margin-top:14px">
              <div class="st-card-hdr">
                <div class="st-card-icon" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0891b2,#0e7490)">
                  <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5"/><polyline points="21 15 16 10 5 21"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--d-text);">Foto Hero Portal Pelanggan</div>
                  <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--d-muted);">Background gambar di halaman login portal customer</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="st-card-body">
                <!-- Preview -->
                <div class="pf-field">
                  <label class="pf-label">Preview</label>
                  <div id="portalHeroPreview" style="position:relative;width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/10;max-height:240px;border:1.5px dashed var(--d-border);border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;background:#f8fafc;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;">
                    <!-- diisi JS -->
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap">
                  <label class="pf-btn-outline" style="flex:1;min-width:140px;cursor:pointer;">
                    <svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 16v2a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2v-2M16 8l-4-4m0 0L8 8m4-4v12"/></svg>
                    Pilih Gambar
                    <input type="file" id="portalHeroInput" accept="image/png,image/jpeg,image/webp" style="display:none" onchange="onPortalHeroPicked(event)">
                  </label>
                  <button class="pf-btn-outline" style="color:#dc2626;border-color:#fecaca;" onclick="deletePortalHero()">
                    <svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="3 6 5 6 21 6"/><path d="M19 6v14a2 2 0 01-2 2H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V6m3 0V4a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v2"/></svg>
                    Hapus
                  </button>
                </div>
                <div class="pf-hint">Format PNG/JPG/WebP · max 4MB · rekomendasi rasio 3:2 atau 16:10 · resolusi minimum 1200px.</div>

                <!-- Overlay opacity slider -->
                <div class="pf-field" style="margin-top:14px">
                  <label class="pf-label">Opacity Overlay Biru</label>
                  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px">
                    <input type="range" id="portalHeroOverlay" min="0" max="1" step="0.05" value="0.55" style="flex:1" oninput="document.getElementById('portalHeroOverlayVal').textContent=this.value">
                    <span id="portalHeroOverlayVal" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--d-text);font-family:monospace;min-width:36px;text-align:center;">0.55</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="pf-hint">0 = foto terlihat jelas, 1 = overlay biru penuh. Rekomendasi 0.45-0.65.</div>
                </div>

                <!-- Welcome title & subtitle -->
                <div class="pf-field" style="margin-top:10px">
                  <label class="pf-label">Welcome Title <span style="color:var(--d-muted);font-weight:400">(opsional)</span></label>
                  <input type="text" class="pf-input" id="portalWelcomeTitle" placeholder="Welcome Back">
                </div>
                <div class="pf-field">
                  <label class="pf-label">Welcome Subtitle <span style="color:var(--d-muted);font-weight:400">(opsional)</span></label>
                  <input type="text" class="pf-input" id="portalWelcomeSub" placeholder="Masukkan detail akun Anda">
                </div>

                <button class="save-btn" onclick="savePortalHeroSettings()" style="margin-top:6px">
                  <svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                  Simpan Pengaturan
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- GENERAL SECTION -->
          <div class="st-section" id="sec-general">
            <div class="st-card">
              <div class="st-card-hdr">
                <div class="st-card-icon"><svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M12 2v3m0 14v3M4.22 4.22l2.12 2.12m11.32 11.32l2.12 2.12M2 12h3m14 0h3M4.22 19.78l2.12-2.12M17.66 6.34l2.12-2.12"/></svg></div>
                <div>
                  <div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--d-text);">Pengaturan Umum</div>
                  <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--d-muted);">Konfigurasi dasar sistem</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="st-card-body">
                <div class="pf-field">
                  <label class="pf-label">Nama Perusahaan</label>
                  <input type="text" class="pf-input" id="companyName" value="<%= appSettings?.company_name||'' %>" placeholder="PT. Nama Perusahaan">
                </div>
                <div class="pf-field">
                  <label class="pf-label">Nomor WhatsApp Customer Service</label>
                  <input type="text" class="pf-input" id="companyWhatsapp" value="<%= appSettings?.company_whatsapp||'' %>" placeholder="6281234567890">
                  <div class="pf-hint">Nomor yang akan dibuka saat customer klik tombol konfirmasi pembayaran. Format: kode negara tanpa '+' (contoh: <b>6281234567890</b>).</div>
                </div>
                <div class="pf-field">
                  <label class="pf-label">SNMP Community</label>
                  <input type="text" class="pf-input" id="snmpCommunity" value="<%= appSettings?.snmp_community||'public' %>">
                </div>
                <div class="pf-field">
                  <label class="pf-label">Poll Interval (detik)</label>
                  <input type="number" class="pf-input" id="pollInterval" value="<%= appSettings?.poll_interval||'60' %>" min="10" max="300">
                </div>
                <button class="save-btn" onclick="saveGeneralSettings()">
                  <svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                  Simpan Pengaturan
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- PAYMENT SECTION -->
          <div class="st-section" id="sec-payment">

            <!-- ═══ PPN / TAX CONFIG ═══ -->
            <div class="st-card" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
              <div class="st-card-hdr">
                <div class="st-card-icon" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d9488,#0f766e);">
                  <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 8h6M9 12h6M9 16h3M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div style="flex:1">
                  <div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--d-text);">PPN / Pajak</div>
                  <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--d-muted);">Atur tarif PPN yang otomatis ditambahkan pada tagihan baru</div>
                </div>
                <label style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;cursor:pointer;user-select:none;position:relative;">
                  <span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--d-text);" id="taxEnabledLbl"><%= (appSettings?.tax_enabled === '1' || appSettings?.tax_enabled === 'true') ? 'Aktif' : 'Nonaktif' %></span>
                  <input type="checkbox" id="taxEnabled" <%= (appSettings?.tax_enabled === '1' || appSettings?.tax_enabled === 'true') ? 'checked' : '' %> onchange="onTaxEnabledChange()" style="position:absolute;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;">
                  <span class="tax-switch"></span>
                </label>
              </div>
              <div class="st-card-body" id="taxCardBody" style="padding:16px 20px">
                <div style="background:#f0fdfa;border:1px solid #99f6e4;border-radius:10px;padding:11px 14px;margin-bottom:14px;display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;font-size:12px;color:#115e59;line-height:1.55;">
                  <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"/></svg>
                  <div>
                    PPN ini diterapkan otomatis saat <b>generate tagihan baru</b>. Tagihan yang sudah dibuat tidak berubah. Pastikan tarif sesuai aturan pajak terbaru (PPN umum di Indonesia 11%, beberapa kategori 12% sejak Januari 2025).
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(180px,1fr));gap:14px;margin-bottom:14px;">
                  <div class="pf-field" style="margin:0">
                    <label class="pf-label">Tarif PPN (%)</label>
                    <div style="display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center;">
                      <input type="number" class="pf-input" id="taxRate" value="<%= appSettings?.tax_rate || '11' %>" min="0" max="100" step="0.01" style="flex:1" oninput="updateTaxPreview()">
                      <span style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--d-muted);">%</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pf-hint" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap;">Preset:
                      <button type="button" class="tax-preset" onclick="setTaxRate(11)">11%</button>
                      <button type="button" class="tax-preset" onclick="setTaxRate(12)">12%</button>
                      <button type="button" class="tax-preset" onclick="setTaxRate(0)">0%</button>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="pf-field" style="margin:0">
                    <label class="pf-label">Mode Perhitungan</label>
                    <select class="pf-select" id="taxMode" onchange="updateTaxPreview()">
                      <option value="exclusive" <%= (appSettings?.tax_mode || 'exclusive') === 'exclusive' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Exclusive — Harga + PPN</option>
                      <option value="inclusive" <%= appSettings?.tax_mode === 'inclusive' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Inclusive — Harga sudah termasuk PPN</option>
                    </select>
                  </div>
                  <div class="pf-field" style="margin:0">
                    <label class="pf-label">Label di Invoice</label>
                    <input type="text" class="pf-input" id="taxLabel" value="<%= appSettings?.tax_label || 'PPN' %>" placeholder="PPN" maxlength="30">
                    <div class="pf-hint">Contoh: PPN, VAT, Pajak Layanan</div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Live preview -->
                <div style="background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:10px;padding:14px;">
                  <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#64748b;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;">
                    <svg width="13" height="13" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>
                    Preview Perhitungan
                  </div>
                  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
                    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;">
                      <label style="font-size:12px;color:#64748b;">Harga paket:</label>
                      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:8px;padding:4px 10px;">
                        <span style="font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;">Rp</span>
                        <input type="number" id="taxPreviewBase" value="100000" min="0" step="1000" oninput="updateTaxPreview()" style="border:none;outline:none;width:90px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;">
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="flex:1;min-width:240px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:8px;text-align:right;">
                      <div>
                        <div style="font-size:10px;color:#94a3b8;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;font-weight:700;">Subtotal</div>
                        <div id="taxPrevSubtotal" style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;">Rp 100.000</div>
                      </div>
                      <div>
                        <div style="font-size:10px;color:#0d9488;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;font-weight:700;" id="taxPrevTaxLbl">PPN 11%</div>
                        <div id="taxPrevTax" style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#0d9488;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;">Rp 11.000</div>
                      </div>
                      <div>
                        <div style="font-size:10px;color:#1d4ed8;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;font-weight:700;">Total</div>
                        <div id="taxPrevTotal" style="font-size:14px;font-weight:800;color:#1d4ed8;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;">Rp 111.000</div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:14px;">
                  <button type="button" onclick="recalculateInvoiceTax()" id="recalcTaxBtn" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:8px 13px;border-radius:9px;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;border:1.5px solid #cbd5e1;background:#fff;color:#475569;transition:all .15s;font-family:inherit;" onmouseover="this.style.background='#f8fafc'" onmouseout="this.style.background='#fff'" title="Terapkan setting PPN saat ini ke invoice yang masih unpaid/overdue">
                    <svg width="13" height="13" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/></svg>
                    Recalculate ke Invoice Unpaid
                  </button>
                  <button class="save-btn" onclick="saveTaxSettings()">
                    <svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                    Simpan PPN
                  </button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- ═══ AUTO GENERATE INVOICE ═══ -->
            <div class="st-card" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
              <div class="st-card-hdr">
                <div class="st-card-icon" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2563eb,#1d4ed8);">
                  <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="16" r="2.5" fill="#fff"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div style="flex:1">
                  <div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--d-text);">Auto Generate Invoice</div>
                  <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--d-muted);">Otomatis bikin tagihan untuk semua pelanggan aktif tiap awal bulan</div>
                </div>
                <label style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;cursor:pointer;user-select:none;position:relative;">
                  <span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--d-text);" id="autoGenLbl"><%= (appSettings?.auto_generate_invoice === '0' || appSettings?.auto_generate_invoice === 'false') ? 'Nonaktif' : 'Aktif' %></span>
                  <input type="checkbox" id="autoGenInvoice" <%= (appSettings?.auto_generate_invoice === '0' || appSettings?.auto_generate_invoice === 'false') ? '' : 'checked' %> onchange="onAutoGenChange()" style="position:absolute;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;">
                  <span class="autogen-switch"></span>
                </label>
              </div>
              <div class="st-card-body" style="padding:14px 20px">
                <div style="background:#eff6ff;border:1px solid #bfdbfe;border-radius:10px;padding:11px 14px;display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;font-size:12px;color:#1e40af;line-height:1.6;">
                  <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
                  <div>
                    Saat aktif, sistem otomatis generate invoice <b>tanggal 1 setiap bulan jam 01:30</b> untuk semua customer dengan status aktif. Periode mengikuti bulan saat itu, due date sesuai <code style="background:#dbeafe;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:4px;font-size:11px;">due_date</code> di profil customer.
                    <br>Kalau server di-restart di tengah bulan dan periode bulan ini belum di-generate sama sekali, sistem akan auto catch-up beberapa detik setelah server start.
                    <br><b style="color:#0d9488">Idempotent</b> — invoice yang sudah ada tidak akan di-duplikasi.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

