                    <li>Settings → <b>Access Keys</b> → copy <b>Server Key</b> & <b>Client Key</b></li>
                    <li>Paste ke form di atas → simpan</li>
                    <li>Settings → <b>Configuration</b> → set <b>Payment Notification URL</b> = URL webhook di atas</li>
                    <li>Test dengan invoice di portal customer (mode sandbox dulu)</li>
                  </ol>
                </div>
                <div id="setupGuideXendit" class="setup-guide" style="display:none">
                  <ol style="margin:0;padding-left:22px;font-size:12.5px;color:var(--d-text);line-height:1.85">
                    <li>Daftar akun di <a href="https://dashboard.xendit.co" target="_blank" style="color:var(--d-blue1);font-weight:700">dashboard.xendit.co</a></li>
                    <li>Lengkapi data perusahaan & aktivasi (untuk production)</li>
